{"tid":2274834,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"現代魔戒真知晶球","createTime":"2020-11-06T16:45:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T10:18:57.000Z","uid":300630,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7439139638dea09da40765fea188195088aca75d","tid":2274834,"uid":300630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T16:45:30.000Z","msg":"真知晶球（Palant&iacute;r）（有時稱為魔眼石，但實質的意思是「遠觀」）是一種有點像水晶球的石頭。當某人注視着真知晶球，他可以跟其他注視着真知晶球的人溝通。具有強大法力的人更可以操縱真知晶球，看到世界任何一個角落的景象。真知晶球是諾多族精靈及費諾所造的，他們造了許多真知晶球，實際的數目不明。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9a34c58529fbeab84fe782412cc4f834cad55c0","tid":2274834,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T16:46:13.000Z","msg":"係 好抵買 佢地賺夠先賣大家用"},{"pid":"41325d7ffe50a81fa43fc4835f407db305af94a5","tid":2274834,"uid":300630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9a34c58529fbeab84fe782412cc4f834cad55c0","tid":2274834,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T16:46:13.000Z","msg":"係 好抵買 佢地賺夠先賣大家用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T16:49:57.000Z","msg":"佢哋出極多糧比自己姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n間公司仲蝕緊唔夠錢 咪比個機會大家上船<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c22662ad92d464e180c50a8fc7163b45205bcf90","tid":2274834,"uid":28415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T16:18:51.000Z","msg":"More"},{"pid":"25d8291f275e3ad2858ebbf73db5276af5269c53","tid":2274834,"uid":300630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T16:54:20.000Z","msg":"推推推<br />\n為Palantir 狂歡吧"},{"pid":"c1932f1a633c723bd01b16276e7b39ce1f4d018e","tid":2274834,"uid":300630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T16:55:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a887d525a33d43e4b8dbbef6686bf81fda32271","tid":2274834,"uid":300630,"like":0,"dislike"